.Dd February 26, 1993
.Dt WIRE-TEST 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm wire-test
.Nd test your network interfaces and local IP address
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Ar host
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
is used to find out what
.Nm Amd
thinks are the first two network interfaces and network names/numbers
used, as well as the IP address used for
.Nm Amd
to NFS-mount itself.
.Pp
If
.Ar host
is specified, then
.Nm
will test for the working combinations of
.Tn NFS
protocol and version from the current client to the
.Tn NFS
server
.Ar host .
If not specified,
.Ar host
defaults to
.Dq localhost .
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr amd 8
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
utility appeared in
.Fx 3.0 .
